        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好啦，快走了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有时间多问，我被芬妮拉着登上离开零区的装甲车。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在慌慌张张地清洗消毒更衣以及疑似超速的车程之后，我们终于赶到了舞会会场。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而且极限到达没有迟到，对于这个结果，芬妮显然很是满足。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在车上的时候，偶尔能看到芬妮露出些微痛苦的表情，甚至下意识去揉自己的脚踝……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但每当我问起，她都会立马笑着将话题转移开来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "准备好了吗？",
        "disable": 0
